text: Slepche () is a village in Municipality of Dolneni, central North Macedonia.Link to the article at Makedonija. Village is located on the northwestern part of Municipality of Dolneni. ==Demographics== As of 2002, the village has 68 inhabitants and the ethnic composition was the following: * Macedonians - 67 * Serbs - 1 == References == Category:Villages in Dolneni Municipality
